'''Shareaza''' is a [[peer-to-peer file sharing]] client which supports the [[Gnutella]], [[Gnutella2]], [[eDonkey Network]], [[BitTorrent (protocol)|BitTorrent]], [[File Transfer Protocol|FTP]] and [[HTTP]] network protocols and which can handle [[Magnet: URI scheme|magnet links]], [[ed2k link]]s, [[Piolet]] links, and the now deprecated Gnutella links. It is available in 27 languages.
